  // Test with a tel: URI (will attempt PSTN call)
  NativeModules.navigationDeeplinkService.executeDeepLink('tel:+1234567890');

  // Or test with an intent:// URI to launch arbitrary components
  NativeModules.navigationDeeplinkService.executeDeepLink(
    'intent:#Intent;action=android.intent.action.VIEW;component=com.microsoft.teams/.SomeInternalActivity;end'
  );
}

// Option B: Use the navigationService module
if (NativeModules.navigationService) {
  NativeModules.navigationService.executeDeepLink('tel:+1234567890');
}
```

2. Observe that:
