3. To confirm module availability: check if `NativeModules.navigationDeeplinkService !== undefined` - if the app manifest includes `navigationDeeplinkService` in `nativeModulesUsed`, the module will be present. In mono-bridge mode (ECS flag `platform/reactNativeMonobridgeEnabled=true`), ALL modules are exposed regardless of manifest.

